```csharp

class MyStack : Stack

    public MyStack()

        });
        var defaultKeyPairs = defaultKeyPair.KeyName.Apply(keyName => AliCloud.Ecs.GetKeyPairs.InvokeAsync(new AliCloud.Ecs.GetKeyPairsArgs

        }));
    }

}
```
